            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6 and boil half kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based<strong> oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Crush the <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing it with the side of a knife and remove the skin<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
